Hamilton, Appellant, v. Gibbs et al., Respondents. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November 14, 1890.) Appeal from city court, general term.

Argued before Daly, C. J., and Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

Ely & Walker, for appellant. J. D. Hallen, for respondents.

No opinion. Interlocutory judgment affirmed, with costs. Affirming 10 N. Y. Supp. 521.
